    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "書き初め……か\nそういえば、こころは習っていたんだよな",
      "startTime": 3.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですよ～\nそれなりに自信はあるんですよ？",
      "startTime": 8.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、ちょうど道具もあるし\nせっかくだからやってみるか",
      "startTime": 13.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "え、どうして道具があるんですか？",
      "startTime": 15.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "もう何年も前の話だけど、麻奈と遙子さん、それに\n三枝さんと俺の四人で書き初めをしたことがあったんだ",
      "startTime": 22.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんがいた頃……ですか",
      "startTime": 27.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだよ。懐かしいな\n道具はオフィスに置いてあるはずだから、行こうか",
      "startTime": 35.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あったあった、これだな",
      "startTime": 41.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "おお～、めずらしいですね\nすぐに探し物を見つけられるなんて",
      "startTime": 47.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺をなんだと思って……いや\n結構身に覚えがあるな",
      "startTime": 53.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "年末は沙季ちゃんに仕切られて\nみっちり大掃除をしてましたね",
      "startTime": 58.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "みんなのレッスンと比べるのはおこがましいけど\n信じられないくらい疲れたよ……",
      "startTime": 64.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "出来るマネージャーなのにどこか抜けてる……だから\n莉央さんも世話を焼いちゃうんでしょうね～",
      "startTime": 71.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、{user}さんの\nズボラエピソードをとっても楽しそうに話すんですよ？",
      "startTime": 76.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それはちょっと、というかかなり恥ずかしいな……\n今年はもう少し気を付けないと",
      "startTime": 84.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなお話をしてる間に……は～い\nセッティング完了です！",
      "startTime": 91.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "参考までに聞きたいんですけど\n前に書き初めした時はどんな言葉を書いたんですか？",
      "startTime": 95.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんのは印象的だったな。『商売繁盛』って\nいう字をなんとも言えない表情で書いてたから……",
      "startTime": 103.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "あら～……大変だったとは\n本人からも聞いたことありますけど……",
      "startTime": 110.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃は本当に苦労をかけたよ……",
      "startTime": 113.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14199.999999999989,
          "startTime": 128.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、とりあえず参考になりました\nよーし、よっ、ほっ……はい、出来ました！",
      "startTime": 120.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "『一日一イタズラ』\n遙子さんの何を参考にしたんだ、こころは……",
      "startTime": 130.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "佐伯せんぱいはアイドル活動の目標を書いた訳ですから\nこころもこれを目標にすれば問題ありません！",
      "startTime": 138.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃんへのイタズラをショート動画にまとめれば\nバズること間違いなしですよ～",
      "startTime": 144.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ほどほどにな……それより本当に字がうまくて驚いたよ\nこういう格言があるのかって一瞬信じそうになるな",
      "startTime": 153.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはなんて\n書いたんですか？",
      "startTime": 158.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2599.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 161.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……『健康第一』……",
      "startTime": 161.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのみんなの健康管理も俺の仕事だからな",
      "startTime": 166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはほんと\nブレませんねぇ～",
      "startTime": 172.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "字もうまくもなければ下手でもない……\nやっぱり{user}さんらしいです！",
      "startTime": 178.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "悪かったな、平凡で……",
      "startTime": 181.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "さて、おふざけはこれくらいにして\n本番といきますか～",
      "startTime": 187.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりふざけてたんじゃないか",
      "startTime": 189.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_02-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "よっ、ほっ……出来ました！",
      "startTime": 191.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
